@@yVigilance@@W                                    Racial passive (WIS 22)

Vigilance is a racial passive skill granted to characters with WIS 22 or
higher. It increases dodge and parry chance based on Wisdom, representing
combat anticipation through perceptive depth.

@@yEffect:@@W +WIS*2/5 to dodge and parry chance (@@w+8 at WIS 22@@W).

@@yRaces with Vigilance:@@W Khenari, Deltari, Ushabti, Kethari.

Vigilance is not Sentinel-specific — any class with WIS 22 benefits.
A Cleric with Vigilance dodges more. A Paladin with Vigilance parries more.
A Sentinel with Vigilance dodges more @@wand@@W builds testimony faster from
the increased avoidance.

@@yStat-22 melee passives:@@W
